06:36.395 --> 06:39.440
with that woman.

06:39.482 --> 06:41.735
I thought you made

06:39.482 --> 06:41.735
some good points.

06:41.776 --> 06:44.154
It doesn't matter.

06:41.776 --> 06:44.154
