07:12.766 --> 07:14.142
You know you like it soft.

07:14.184 --> 07:15.643
No, I don't.

07:14.184 --> 07:15.643
Yes, you do.

07:15.685 --> 07:18.563
In fact, so do we.

07:15.685 --> 07:18.563
We all do.

07:18.605 --> 07:19.480
