08:04.067 --> 08:06.111
Oh, look at you!

08:04.067 --> 08:06.111
Come here!

08:06.153 --> 08:07.528
I can't believe it!

08:07.570 --> 08:09.448
How long

08:07.570 --> 08:09.448
