08:09.489 --> 08:10.949
A few days.

08:09.489 --> 08:10.949
Are you surprised?

08:10.991 --> 08:12.326
Surprised?

08:10.991 --> 08:12.326
I'm in shock!

08:12.367 --> 08:13.534
Well, you should be.

08:13.576 --> 08:15.536
I've been planning

08:13.576 --> 08:15.536
