08:22.377 --> 08:24.545
Everybody, this is Piama.

08:24.587 --> 08:27.507
She's my wife.

08:32.095 --> 08:34.014
We're married.

08:34.055 --> 08:35.556
Hi.

08:35.598 --> 08:37.558
I was going to tell you

08:35.598 --> 08:37.558
