08:37.600 --> 08:39.727
and then I thought

08:37.600 --> 08:39.727
why not bring her down here

08:39.769 --> 08:41.188
and surprise you

08:39.769 --> 08:41.188
in person?

08:41.229 --> 08:42.605
What do you mean

08:41.229 --> 08:42.605
you're married?

08:42.647 --> 08:44.565
Piama and I are

08:42.647 --> 08:44.565
husband and wife.

08:44.607 --> 08:45.817
We got married last week.

08:45.859 --> 08:46.860
Last week?

08:46.901 --> 08:48.569
Francis, who is this woman?

08:48.611 --> 08:51.823
She's my wife.

08:48.611 --> 08:51.823
Her name is Piama.

08:51.865 --> 08:54.034
Hello.

08:57.620 --> 08:58.579
Well, come on.

08:58.621 --> 09:00.581
Isn't anyone going

08:58.621 --> 09:00.581
to congratulate us?

09:00.623 --> 09:01.582
What?

09:01.624 --> 09:02.834
For getting married.

09:02.876 --> 09:04.585
That's what families do.

09:04.627 --> 09:05.628
I think I'm going

09:04.627 --> 09:05.628
to be sick.

09:05.670 --> 09:06.838
Well, come on, Mom.

09:06.880 --> 09:08.589
