09:17.640 --> 09:19.600
would be excited

09:17.640 --> 09:19.600
to meet my wife.

09:19.642 --> 09:21.311
I can't believe you guys!

09:21.353 --> 09:23.604
Come on, Francis,

09:21.353 --> 09:23.604
it's not their fault.

09:23.646 --> 09:24.689
What did you expect?

09:24.731 --> 09:26.525
You could have at least

09:24.731 --> 09:26.525
