09:35.325 --> 09:36.535
How long have you

09:35.325 --> 09:36.535
known each other?

09:36.576 --> 09:37.618
You never mentioned her.

09:37.660 --> 09:40.621
I only met her

09:37.660 --> 09:40.621
a month ago... today.

09:40.663 --> 09:42.499
Happy anniversary.

09:42.541 --> 09:43.666
Plus we had

09:42.541 --> 09:43.666
the whole bus ride down.

09:43.708 --> 09:46.627
A month?

09:43.708 --> 09:46.627
I misjudged you.

09:46.669 --> 09:48.629
You know, come to think of it,

09:46.669 --> 09:48.629
that's the longest

09:48.671 --> 09:51.216
you ever stuck with anything

09:48.671 --> 09:51.216
in your life.

09:51.258 --> 09:52.633
Congratulations.

09:52.675 --> 09:53.885
You outlasted

09:52.675 --> 09:53.885
