Turquoise.

15:56.623 --> 15:57.998
Francis got it for me.

15:58.040 --> 15:59.959
Oh.

16:04.464 --> 16:06.006
How was your flight?

16:06.048 --> 16:07.258
We took the bus.

16:07.300 --> 16:09.176
That's right,

16:07.300 --> 16:09.176
I guess that's what Francis did

16:09.218 --> 16:11.262
with the money that I sent him

16:09.218 --> 16:11.262
for his plane fare.

