16:33.075 --> 16:35.035
explaining to you.

16:35.077 --> 16:36.329
Admit it.

16:36.370 --> 16:38.247
You don't like me.

16:38.289 --> 16:39.540
I don't even know you.

16:39.582 --> 16:42.042
Well, what would you like

16:39.582 --> 16:42.042
to know?

16:42.084 --> 16:44.044
I'm 19.

16:44.086 --> 16:45.672
My mom ran off when I was three

16:45.713 --> 16:48.048
and my dad kicked me

16:45.713 --> 16:48.048
out of the house when I was 14

16:48.090 --> 16:49.550
because I threw out his liquor.

16:49.592 --> 16:51.051
I've been married

16:49.592 --> 16:51.051
once before,

16:51.093 --> 16:53.137
no kids, thank God,

16:53.179 --> 16:55.682
and last year,

16:53.179 --> 16:55.682
I spent three weeks in jail

16:55.723 --> 16:57.642
but it wasn't my fault.

16:57.684 --> 16:58.768
Will you stop this, please?

16:58.810 --> 17:00.060
You just can't stand

17:00.102 --> 17:03.105
