17:00.102 --> 17:03.105
to marry beneath him.

17:03.147 --> 17:05.566
What?

17:05.608 --> 17:08.152
Just because

17:05.608 --> 17:08.152
I'm not all classy like you.

17:08.194 --> 17:09.696
Classy?

17:09.737 --> 17:11.489
You think I'm classy?

17:11.531 --> 17:13.073
Don't laugh at me.

17:13.115 --> 17:14.074
I'm sorry.

17:14.116 --> 17:15.284
It's just, this is a first.

17:15.326 --> 17:17.996
I hate to break it to you,

17:15.326 --> 17:17.996
but I am not classy.

17:18.037 --> 17:19.079
Oh, yeah.

17:19.121 --> 17:21.123
You know,

17:19.121 --> 17:21.123
I guess what you call class

17:21.165 --> 17:23.835
I call manners.

17:27.129 --> 17:31.091
I came down here

17:27.129 --> 17:31.091
hoping to get along with you,

17:31.133 --> 17:35.680
but you're not

17:31.133 --> 17:35.680
going to let that happen.

17:35.722 --> 17:41.101
