17:41.143 --> 17:45.523
So, what's going to happen?

17:45.565 --> 17:48.192
I don't know.

17:48.234 --> 17:51.070
What is going to happen?

17:53.948 --> 17:55.115
Good news.

17:55.157 --> 17:57.535
The boys stole my credit card.

17:57.577 --> 17:59.954
All we have to do is call

17:57.577 --> 17:59.954
the credit card company and...

18:01.539 --> 18:03.123
You want to come

18:01.539 --> 18:03.123
outside, baby,

18:01.539 --> 18:03.123
Honey, why don't we go...

18:03.165 --> 18:05.084
and I'll show you

18:03.165 --> 18:05.084
my tree house?

