(gasps)

18:18.556 --> 18:19.849
(grunts)

18:19.891 --> 18:21.141
(screams)

18:21.183 --> 18:22.142
Hello, Malcolm.

18:22.184 --> 18:24.604
(Malcolm groans)

18:22.184 --> 18:24.604
Hi, Mom. Hi, Dad.

18:26.606 --> 18:28.148
Beat it, Vicky.

18:28.190 --> 18:31.360
We'll finish

18:28.190 --> 18:31.360
