18:32.987 --> 18:34.321
Okay, boys,

18:32.987 --> 18:34.321
get your things.

18:34.363 --> 18:35.990
We're going home.

18:36.032 --> 18:38.158
No, we're not

18:36.032 --> 18:38.158
going back there.

18:38.200 --> 18:40.160
Well, you can't stay

18:38.200 --> 18:40.160
in this hotel room forever.

18:40.202 --> 18:41.370
What are you going to do--

18:41.412 --> 18:43.957
live under a bridge and

18:41.412 --> 18:43.957
steal food out of Dumpsters?

18:43.998 --> 18:45.416
I don't know,

18:43.998 --> 18:45.416
but we're not going home.

18:45.458 --> 18:47.167
We've had it with

18:45.458 --> 18:47.167
the way you treat us

18:47.209 --> 18:48.168
and we've had it

18:48.210 --> 18:49.169
with all the yelling!

18:49.211 --> 18:51.089
You are a terrible influence

18:49.211 --> 18:51.089
on us!

18:51.130 --> 18:52.757
All you ever do is scream!

18:52.799 --> 18:54.383
And order us around!

18:54.425 --> 18:56.176
There's something wrong

18:54.425 --> 18:56.176
with this family!

18:56.218 --> 18:57.470
Families should have

18:57.511 --> 19:00.180
some way of communicating

18:57.511 --> 19:00.180
besides yelling!

19:00.222 --> 19:03.267
Okay, everybody,

19:00.222 --> 19:03.267
calm down.

19:03.309 --> 19:05.103
I understand what you're saying.

19:05.144 --> 19:06.562
I am not going to yell.

19:06.604 --> 19:08.355
I am not going to scream.

19:08.397 --> 19:10.190
We are capable

19:08.397 --> 19:10.190
of talking about this

19:10.232 --> 19:12.026
without raising our voices.

19:13.486 --> 19:14.904
Now, boys,

19:13.486 --> 19:14.904
I want you to understand

19:14.946 --> 19:16.489
I am sorry about

19:14.946 --> 19:16.489
what happened,

19:16.530 --> 19:19.867
but you have to understand

19:16.530 --> 19:19.867
I get a little emotional

19:19.909 --> 19:21.911
when I learned

19:19.909 --> 19:21.911
that my oldest son

19:21.953 --> 19:23.496
was acting like an idiot

19:23.537 --> 19:25.123
and throwing his life away.

19:25.164 --> 19:26.540
Now, that doesn't mean...

19:29.919 --> 19:32.379
Stop talking

19:29.919 --> 19:32.379
about him like that!

19:32.421 --> 19:34.548
Francis is my heart!

19:42.140 --> 19:44.017
Okay, we're even.

19:44.058 --> 19:46.393
Everyone's fine and there's

19:44.058 --> 19:46.393
no need for escalation.

19:46.435 --> 19:48.228
Isn't it beautiful

19:46.435 --> 19:48.228
when things work out?

19:48.270 --> 19:50.064
Yeah, I'd say this

19:48.270 --> 19:50.064
