19:51.899 --> 19:53.526
for a better ending.

19:53.567 --> 19:58.238
Get your wife out of my sight.

20:01.117 --> 20:02.743
She called you my wife.

20:02.785 --> 20:04.871
That's progress.

20:07.289 --> 20:09.750
So Dad's birthday

20:07.289 --> 20:09.750
